description: Downloads the regional Amazon Lightsail default key pair. This action also creates a Lightsail default key pair if a default key pair does not currently exist in the Amazon Web Services Region.

nested_items.name: publicKeyBase64
nested_items.description: A base64-encoded public key of the ssh-rsa type.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp when the default key pair was created.
